  "text": "McChesney, [CITATION_1] have analyzed the role of advertising in reinforcing the \"buy now, pay later\" ethos that the financial sector needed for its expansion. The same analysis is advanced by [CITATION_2] . [CITATION_3] argues that real estate advertising encouraged homeowners to remortgage their homes. Nichols (2010a, 2010b) argue that the economic crisis has made apparent a crisis of news journalism.",
